data.description: Priced LOW and READY to GO!! Home has a gleaming pre-inspection. Priced below appraisal, plus offering a $1,500 BUYERS AGENT BONUS! Don't miss out! Step inside, and you'll immediately appreciate the warmth of the home, accentuated by the new furnace installed in 2023, ensuring cozy winters and efficient energy use. The kitchen was upgraded with stunning quartz countertops. The main floor bathrooms were also upgraded with beautiful ceramic tile. The basement boasts a spacious rec room, adorned with a custom wall treatment. It also features a wet bar, with quartz countertops, & a beverage cooler for the ultimate entertainment experience. Step outside into the fully fenced backyard, complete w/a new privacy fence & fire pit, offering a blank canvas to design the outdoor oasis of your dreams. Embrace the outdoor lifestyle as you take a quick walk to the nearby park, disc golf course, or splash pad. Experience the charm of small-town living in this beautifully modern home. Come see it, NOW!
